00:23:02.915 --> 00:23:04.350 align:middle line:90%
to blow apart at the seams

00:23:04.350 --> 00:23:07.120 align:middle line:84%
because of some kind
of internal conflict.

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:10.590 align:middle line:84%
And so let's talk about now the
book, Healing a Broken World.

00:23:10.590 --> 00:23:12.725 align:middle line:84%
We can see how the
world became broken.

00:23:12.725 --> 00:23:15.261 align:middle line:84%
We're still suffering
from the vestiges

00:23:15.261 --> 00:23:17.296 align:middle line:90%
of that kind of oppression.

00:23:17.296 --> 00:23:19.665 align:middle line:84%
We're starting to find our way
out of it I think mentally,

00:23:19.665 --> 00:23:21.033 align:middle line:90%
emotionally and spiritually.

00:23:21.033 --> 00:23:24.403 align:middle line:84%
But still could use a little
helping hand, a little guidance.

00:23:24.403 --> 00:23:27.473 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about Healing a
Broken World and how that came

00:23:27.473 --> 00:23:31.043 align:middle line:84%
through Daniel Raphael
who is the primary author.

00:23:31.043 --> 00:23:32.745 align:middle line:84%
You're the co-author
of this book.

00:23:32.745 --> 00:23:34.080 align:middle line:90%
>> Belitsos: Correct.

00:23:34.080 --> 00:23:37.016 align:middle line:84%
Daniel is part of something
called the Teaching Mission

00:23:37.016 --> 00:23:38.918 align:middle line:84%
which is part of something
called the Correcting Time.

00:23:38.918 --> 00:23:41.788 align:middle line:84%
And the Correcting Time was
launched after the Urantia Book.

00:23:41.788 --> 00:23:42.855 align:middle line:90%
I forgot to mention this to you.

00:23:42.855 --> 00:23:43.990 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Oh, yes, okay.

00:23:43.990 --> 00:23:45.625 align:middle line:84%
>> Belitsos: So it was
proclaimed by the beings

00:23:45.625 --> 00:23:46.659 align:middle line:90%
who wrote the Urantia Book

00:23:46.659 --> 00:23:49.028 align:middle line:84%
through various channels
that we're back.

00:23:49.028 --> 00:23:51.697 align:middle line:84%
They gave this book,
it was printed,

00:23:51.697 --> 00:23:54.667 align:middle line:84%
it's all over the world, it's
in 10 languages, 12 languages.

00:23:54.667 --> 00:23:56.002 align:middle line:90%
Now there's more to say.

00:23:56.002 --> 00:23:56.869 align:middle line:90%
They have a lot more to say.

00:23:56.869 --> 00:23:58.004 align:middle line:90%
Things have changed.

00:23:58.004 --> 00:23:59.305 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: There was a
gap in there I take it?

00:23:59.305 --> 00:24:00.873 align:middle line:84%
>> Belitsos: There was a
generation of things developing.

00:24:00.873 --> 00:24:03.209 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: A generational
gap, okay.

00:24:03.209 --> 00:24:05.178 align:middle line:84%
>> Belitsos: And in
particular they stated,

00:24:05.178 --> 00:24:07.680 align:middle line:84%
and this is controversial
in the Urantia community,

00:24:07.680 --> 00:24:12.084 align:middle line:84%
they stated the Lucifer
rebellion has been ended.

00:24:12.084 --> 00:24:15.788 align:middle line:84%
That is there was a
court case in heaven

00:24:15.788 --> 00:24:19.192 align:middle line:90%
that was settled in 1985.

00:24:19.192 --> 00:24:21.561 align:middle line:90%
And so the end of this --

00:24:21.561 --> 00:24:24.363 align:middle line:84%
there was various
things they terminated,

00:24:24.363 --> 00:24:25.698 align:middle line:84%
certain activities
were terminated

00:24:25.698 --> 00:24:28.067 align:middle line:90%
when Jesus incarnated.

00:24:28.067 --> 00:24:33.206 align:middle line:84%
Many of the key activities were
ended, but there was still more

00:24:33.206 --> 00:24:35.241 align:middle line:84%
to do because they
have to have a case --

00:24:35.241 --> 00:24:38.711 align:middle line:84%
they had to have a judgment
from these higher beings.

00:24:38.711 --> 00:24:41.814 align:middle line:84%
And that was handed down in
85 kind of right in the midst

00:24:41.814 --> 00:24:45.051 align:middle line:84%
of the worst part
of the cold war.

00:24:45.051 --> 00:24:47.854 align:middle line:84%
And they had no way
to let us know other

00:24:47.854 --> 00:24:49.522 align:middle line:90%
than through channels.

00:24:49.522 --> 00:24:52.391 align:middle line:84%
So this came through all
these different groups all

00:24:52.391 --> 00:24:53.526 align:middle line:90%
over the place.

00:24:53.526 --> 00:24:55.461 align:middle line:84%
And so we just had to
like say if it's coming

00:24:55.461 --> 00:24:57.563 align:middle line:84%
through all these people
independently it must be true.

00:24:57.563 --> 00:25:00.366 align:middle line:84%
So it's known as
the adjudication

00:25:00.366 --> 00:25:01.801 align:middle line:90%
of the Lucifer rebellion.

00:25:01.801 --> 00:25:04.303 align:middle line:84%
And with that they
announced the Correcting Time

00:25:04.303 --> 00:25:05.438 align:middle line:90%
which has two parts.

00:25:05.438 --> 00:25:09.075 align:middle line:84%
One part is using the
Urantia lingo to teach.

00:25:09.075 --> 00:25:12.545 align:middle line:84%
And the other part is teaching
without the Urantia lingo

00:25:12.545 --> 00:25:16.249 align:middle line:84%
which is the main part where
the angelic host is now

00:25:16.249 --> 00:25:20.386 align:middle line:84%
rehabilitated, is
working to end communism.

00:25:20.386 --> 00:25:22.755 align:middle line:84%
And they actually say
it was part of our work

00:25:22.755 --> 00:25:24.557 align:middle line:84%
that brought an end
to the cold war

00:25:24.557 --> 00:25:27.460 align:middle line:84%
because there were angelic
appearances to Gorbachev.

00:25:27.460 --> 00:25:28.661 align:middle line:90%
You may have heard this.

00:25:28.661 --> 00:25:30.096 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: No, I have
never heard that actually.

00:25:30.096 --> 00:25:34.367 align:middle line:84%
>> Belitsos: Just a whole play,
it's documentation of the fact

00:25:34.367 --> 00:25:39.372 align:middle line:84%
that the had two angels that
came to him and worked with him.

00:25:39.372 --> 00:25:41.173 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, you can look
that up and see that.

00:25:41.173 --> 00:25:44.010 align:middle line:84%
And it was just a lot of
influence by a certain type

00:25:44.010 --> 00:25:46.512 align:middle line:84%
of angel that can
work on social change,

00:25:46.512 --> 00:25:48.915 align:middle line:84%
they have like angels
of social change.

00:25:48.915 --> 00:25:51.350 align:middle line:84%
So they said a lot of
these things you're seeing

00:25:51.350 --> 00:25:56.055 align:middle line:84%
around you are work
co-creative, not just us.

00:25:56.055 --> 00:25:57.189 align:middle line:90%
We're working through you.

00:25:57.189 --> 00:25:59.292 align:middle line:84%
When you're ready
then we work with you.

00:25:59.292 --> 00:26:01.394 align:middle line:84%
When you get the idea
we enhance the idea.

00:26:01.394 --> 00:26:03.963 align:middle line:84%
We don't necessarily
give you the idea

00:26:03.963 --> 00:26:05.298 align:middle line:84%
because we're not really
allowed to do that.

00:26:05.298 --> 00:26:06.699 align:middle line:90%
It has to be your idea.

00:26:06.699 --> 00:26:10.169 align:middle line:84%
But then we tweak it and improve
the idea and enhance the idea.

00:26:10.169 --> 00:26:14.106 align:middle line:84%
So the many movements
that we see now

00:26:14.106 --> 00:26:16.008 align:middle line:84%
like the environmental
movement, for example,

00:26:16.008 --> 00:26:17.910 align:middle line:84%
they say we're a
part of that, too.

00:26:17.910 --> 00:26:20.046 align:middle line:84%
Everything positive
we're a part of.

00:26:20.046 --> 00:26:24.317 align:middle line:84%
But we still have a battle
against the Luciferic party

00:26:24.317 --> 00:26:26.619 align:middle line:84%
which are the humans
that were part

00:26:26.619 --> 00:26:28.754 align:middle line:90%
of these Illuminati families.

00:26:28.754 --> 00:26:33.125 align:middle line:84%
And they're still wealthy,
active, but we're cleaning it

00:26:33.125 --> 00:26:34.727 align:middle line:90%
up but it's taking time.

00:26:34.727 --> 00:26:37.063 align:middle line:84%
So that's why you see
this back and forth.

00:26:37.063 --> 00:26:40.333 align:middle line:84%
Things are going well for
a while then 9/11 happens.

00:26:40.333 --> 00:26:45.237 align:middle line:84%
And that is in my humble opinion
not just a secular thing.

00:26:45.237 --> 00:26:46.339 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Exactly.

00:26:46.339 --> 00:26:48.507 align:middle line:84%
>> Belitsos: That's
off planet involvement

00:26:48.507 --> 00:26:51.210 align:middle line:90%
to really move us backward.

00:26:51.210 --> 00:26:53.379 align:middle line:84%
Progress went backward
at that point.

00:26:53.379 --> 00:26:55.848 align:middle line:84%
So they're stating
it's a pretty rough go

00:26:55.848 --> 00:26:58.884 align:middle line:84%
because you have very
strong Luciferic leadership

00:26:58.884 --> 00:27:00.119 align:middle line:90%
on the planet.

00:27:00.119 --> 00:27:02.822 align:middle line:84%
It's mainly hidden away but
sometimes not so hidden.

00:27:02.822 --> 00:27:08.894 align:middle line:84%
So we launched yet
another program called the

00:27:08.894 --> 00:27:10.262 align:middle line:90%
Magisterial Mission.

00:27:10.262 --> 00:27:12.331 align:middle line:84%
So that's what this book
is really the first book

00:27:12.331 --> 00:27:13.532 align:middle line:90%
of this mission.

00:27:13.532 --> 00:27:16.002 align:middle line:84%
So there's really two
missions of these beings.

00:27:16.002 --> 00:27:18.537 align:middle line:84%
One is called the
Teaching Mission

00:27:18.537 --> 00:27:20.373 align:middle line:90%
which is spiritual teachings,

00:27:20.373 --> 00:27:23.409 align:middle line:84%
I've published many
books of that.

00:27:23.409 --> 00:27:27.980 align:middle line:84%
And then graduated to a
social transformation teaching

00:27:27.980 --> 00:27:29.949 align:middle line:84%
which I'd never heard of
anything quite like it

00:27:29.949 --> 00:27:32.618 align:middle line:84%
where high beings are
teaching cultural and social

00:27:32.618 --> 00:27:34.954 align:middle line:84%
and political transformation
to individuals.

00:27:34.954 --> 00:27:36.655 align:middle line:90%
