00:29:05.945 --> 00:29:07.279 align:middle line:90%
to do it.

00:29:07.279 --> 00:29:09.949 align:middle line:84%
And many of them are corrupt
and they're part of self --

00:29:09.949 --> 00:29:11.550 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: A lot of them
