And you can't fix it
so don't even think

00:29:36.609 --> 00:29:38.611 align:middle line:90%
about fixing these institutions.

00:29:38.611 --> 00:29:41.046 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: So we're talking
about all the known systems?

00:29:41.046 --> 00:29:42.114 align:middle line:90%
>> Belitsos: Yeah.

00:29:42.114 --> 00:29:43.482 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: Economic,
etc., governmental.

00:29:43.482 --> 00:29:44.483 align:middle line:84%
>> Belitsos: Governmental,
economic.

00:29:44.483 --> 00:29:45.584 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: And so
what did they say

00:29:45.584 --> 00:29:47.052 align:middle line:84%
that collapse will look
like, and what kind

00:29:47.052 --> 00:29:50.189 align:middle line:84%
of time frames are they looking
at before the disintegration

00:29:50.189 --> 00:29:52.591 align:middle line:84%
and then new consciousness,
new systems rising?

