00:32:32.818 --> 00:32:34.920 align:middle line:90%
So he is that type of being.

00:32:34.920 --> 00:32:38.457 align:middle line:84%
He is known as a
magisterial son.

00:32:38.457 --> 00:32:41.927 align:middle line:90%
And they incarnate.

00:32:41.927 --> 00:32:45.164 align:middle line:90%
So this will be an avatar event.

00:32:45.164 --> 00:32:49.034 align:middle line:84%
And so every normal
planet has such a being.

00:32:49.034 --> 00:32:53.372 align:middle line:84%
But because we're not normal
he has a very special program

00:32:53.372 --> 00:32:55.607 align:middle line:90%
adapted for our big problems.

00:32:55.607 --> 00:32:59.545 align:middle line:84%
Normally if a magisterial son
comes things are pretty good,

00:32:59.545 --> 00:33:03.816 align:middle line:84%
and you don't have nuclear wars
and you don't have genocide.

00:33:03.816 --> 00:33:05.317 align:middle line:84%
But you have to really
move forward,

00:33:05.317 --> 00:33:06.819 align:middle line:90%
and you need a world teacher.

00:33:06.819 --> 00:33:10.656 align:middle line:84%
So he becomes the
maitreya, the world teacher.

00:33:10.656 --> 00:33:12.758 align:middle line:84%
And so he incarnates
for that purpose.

00:33:12.758 --> 00:33:16.028 align:middle line:84%
But in this case they have
all these programs most

00:33:16.028 --> 00:33:17.496 align:middle line:90%
of which we don't know about.

00:33:17.496 --> 00:33:21.467 align:middle line:84%
This is just one of them,
it's a big one, though,

00:33:21.467 --> 00:33:25.003 align:middle line:84%
to get grass roots
reconfiguration

00:33:25.003 --> 00:33:28.640 align:middle line:84%
of society creating
this database

