>> Regina: Right.

00:33:50.396 --> 00:33:53.332 align:middle line:84%
>> Belitsos: Or some
capitalist corporation.

00:33:53.332 --> 00:33:54.800 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: It's very
clear and practical.

00:33:54.800 --> 00:33:57.569 align:middle line:84%
Everything I read in there
was very clear and practical

00:33:57.569 --> 00:34:00.372 align:middle line:90%
and beautifully articulated.

00:34:00.372 --> 00:34:01.540 align:middle line:90%
>> Belitsos: Thanks.

00:34:01.540 --> 00:34:04.076 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, I mean these are
very articulate beings.

00:34:04.076 --> 00:34:05.076 align:middle line:90%
Their English is perfect.

00:34:05.076 --> 00:34:07.379 align:middle line:90%
It's just amazing.

00:34:07.379 --> 00:34:09.915 align:middle line:84%
So it makes it easy for us
